Package: meyer
Type: Package
Title: Contains functions for meyerization and prior Student t df determination
Version: 0.1
Date: 2023-12-2
Author: Emil Niclas Meyer-Hansen
Maintainer: Emil Niclas Meyer-Hansen <emil098meyerhansen@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0), stats
Description: Provides novel functions for rescaling vectors as correlation coefficients and qualitatively determining degrees of freedom (df) for a prior Student t-distribution, including simple functions useful for frequentist and Bayesian statisticians.
License: GPL (>=3)
